# Project Requirements

## 1. Functional
1. Secure login via Supabase magic link or email/password.
2. Role-based dashboards and permissions.
3. Bi-directional sync with Google Sheets (≤ 5 min latency).
4. Agents can create/update/delete their leads.
5. Managers can reassign leads within their team.
6. Follow-up scheduling with date picker & notes.
7. Meeting scheduling with calendar view & iCal export.
8. Super Admin can manage users & roles without DB access.

## 2. Non-Functional
* **Performance**: Any screen loads ≤ 200 ms (p95) on broadband, ≤ 1 s on 3G.  
* **Scalability**: Support 10 k leads, 100 concurrent users without degradation.  
* **Security**: OWASP Top 10 compliance, daily automated dependency scanning.  
* **Availability**: 99.5 % uptime SLA.  
* **Compliance**: GDPR (data deletion & export).  
* **Accessibility**: WCAG 2.1 AA.

## 3. Out of Scope (v1)
* SMS integrations.  
* Lead scoring ML model.  

